Package org.opensaml.saml.saml1.binding.artifact

Classes that may be used to create and manipulate SAML 1 artifacts.

See: Description

    Interface Description
    SAML1Artifact
    Interface marker for SAML 1 artifacts.
    SAML1ArtifactBuilder<ArtifactType extends AbstractSAML1Artifact>
    Builder of typed SAML 1 artifacts.
